build I20041221

Did a sync on a linked project.
A file had been added to the remote.
It got an error on this file.
Earlier, I was also getting similar errors on another linked project

It's possible this may be due to a server configuration problem, since this is
on a non-Eclipse, non-IBM CVS repo (Ken's at home).

Last log entry is:

Some of the entries in the rest of the log may be of interest.

The SAXParseException can probably be ignored.  I had tried creating an empty
eTune.launch file, in order to add it under version control and replace from
head, to get around the sync problem (I was unable to do this -- it didn't allow
me to add it under version control since someone else already had).

I assume the repository is running CVSNT. The only supported version of CVSNT 
is 2.0.58d and it must be configured to act like a linux server (1.11.2).
